snippet.title: Super Totally Ultimate Dad Showdown - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a sneak peak at what we have been working on soon!

STUDS is releasing on Steam March 26th: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1570730/Super_Totally_Ultimate_Dad_Showdown/

The Build is live now on Itch.io: https://sandalledsocks.itch.io/dad-showdown
